This task demonstrate using the recursive functions:

gcdRec - returns greatest common divisor;
sumDigits - obviously returns sum of decimal digits of natural number;
numDigits - returns the number of decimal digits of a given natural number
printOddEven - return even or odd number;
hailStone - prints in one line all numbers of the Collatz sequence from n to 1;

For better understanding last function , recommend to read:
https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/hailstone-numbers/


